      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Your comparison to a glitching line of code is a powerful metaphor for the numbness that comes from feeling invisible in a hyper-connected world. It's a valid reaction to being reduced to a profile icon, but the pain of that erasure often stems from the very effort it takes to maintain that connection. You are more than the dots and notifications; your existence is solid and meaningful even when the digital world makes it feel otherwise.",
